{"tid":1571981,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"手足受傷，無地方休息可聯絡","createTime":"2019-09-15T14:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T14:33:29.000Z","uid":256218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"37f4cd3626e62bf2215cf5932bd43a0e6d5a8fe1","tid":1571981,"uid":256218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:33:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=114633119923989&amp;id=107771640610137\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D114633119923989%26id%3D107771640610137&d=02TnLe2cOfQrY9jdqtoXefDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=d49aff13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=114633119923989&amp;id=107771640610137</a><br />\n<br />\n*麻煩廣傳，增加傷者知道嘅機會*<br />\n<br />\n【跟懸壺同步的中醫醫療支援】<br />\n<br />\n今晚非定點義務流動中醫醫療支援開放。<br />\n<br />\n打傷、棍傷、跌撞傷、扭傷<br />\n<br />\n關節脫位、非開放性骨折（唔係插左條骨出來）<br />\n<br />\n皮肉傷口、化學刺激或中毒症狀（嚴重至出血例如鼻血屙血咳血都可處理，氣管、黏膜、皮膚刺激當然也可以。）<br />\n<br />\n無家可歸、未食飯<br />\n<br />\n以上為支援範圍。<br />\n<br />\n病向淺中醫，盡快pm來，手足同行唔講錢，唔使再問診金藥費，全免。<br />\n<br />\n有其他特殊情況也請pm來查詢。<br />\n<br />\n祝大家平安。"}]}